{"tid":1803162,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府委任落選建制議員入食水安全諮詢委員會委員","createTime":"2019-12-30T04:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T07:47:20.000Z","uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c11855e9fb5dc431b0b39684c9f50b21533aca0d","tid":1803162,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:05:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/30/P2019123000212.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201912%2F30%2FP2019123000212.htm&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=ba22e3d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/30/P2019123000212.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府委任食水安全諮詢委員會委員<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  政府今日（十二月三十日）宣布委任食水安全諮詢委員會兩名新成員，以及再度委任現任主席、副主席及十三名成員，任期由二○二○年一月一日起生效，為期兩年。<br />\n   <br />\n  發展局局長黃偉綸說﹕「政府一直非常關注食水安全。我感謝委員過去兩年的支持和貢獻，協助政府推展各項有關食水安全的工作。我期望與委員會繼續合作，就進一步保障香港食水安全制訂全面和切實可行的政策措施。」<br />\n   <br />\n  委員會於二○一八年一月一日成立，就香港食水安全規管制度的制定、香港食水安全標準的檢討，以及與食水安全有關的政策和運作措施向發展局提供意見。此外，委員會亦會檢視世界各地關注的食水安全事宜，以及因應國際常規、趨勢或發展而制定的新研究方向。<br />\n   <br />\n  二○二○年一月一日起委員會的成員名單如下： <br />\n<br />\n主席<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n梁廣灝<br />\n<br />\n副主席<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n陳漢輝博士<br />\n <br />\n非官方成員<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n徐婷芳博士<br />\nDavid Anthony Cunliffe博士<br />\n何建宗教授<br />\n何鉅業<br />\n劉嘉珮教授<br />\n勞敏慈教授<br />\n馬耀華博士<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鄧銘心</span></span><br />\n謝立亞教授<br />\n王紹明醫生<br />\n黃譚智媛醫生<br />\n黃耀新<br />\n <br />\n現任名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.devb.gov.hk/tc/boards_and_committees/drinking_water_safety_advisory_committee/membership/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.devb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fboards_and_committees%2Fdrinking_water_safety_advisory_committee%2Fmembership%2Findex.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=fde86ab3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.devb.gov.hk/tc/boards_and_committees/drinking_water_safety_advisory_committee/membership/index.html</a><br />\n委員會成員名單<br />\n第一屆 (2018年1月1日至2019年12月31日)<br />\n<br />\n主席<br />\n梁廣灝工程師, SBS, JP<br />\n <br />\n副主席<br />\n陳漢輝博士工程師, BBS<br />\n <br />\n非官方委員<br />\nDr CUNLIFFE David Anthony<br />\n何建宗教授, BBS, JP<br />\n何鉅業先生, JP<br />\n劉嘉珮教授<br />\n勞敏慈教授工程師, JP<br />\n馬耀華博士<br />\n謝立亞教授<br />\n王紹明醫生<br />\n黃譚智媛醫生, JP<br />\n黃耀新工程師"},{"pid":"4f2e8e381b6ad9366967b11a445fc03a4a45dd2d","tid":1803162,"uid":6497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:13:46.000Z","msg":"呢D就冇人理"},{"pid":"07ed98621b0b7e6e2164d529ab942422707e2ca9","tid":1803162,"uid":225130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"劉江華做局長都係咁啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c91f29711a799669e3fa2f4b4b5c77f5b124163","tid":1803162,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:15:59.000Z","msg":"班濕鳩少數派死唔斷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c8fcbc5a242acab1f33ed00a4852983da688e5","tid":1803162,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"有冇錢？"},{"pid":"1c16e4295d4201ff35004c0f436157d65f135565","tid":1803162,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"大家幫手宣傳下，ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同你身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sa5sWmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSa5sWmr.jpg&h=2e6a418c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSU2qmP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoSU2qmP.jpg&h=0ee870ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2skMss7.jpg\" data-th